info-config-setup-example:
Example of watch mode setup in mgnl.config.js:
```
  watchMode: {
    CreateModelPlugin: {
      enabled: true,
      watchPaths: ['**/dialogs/**/*.yaml']
    },
    CreateRestEndpointPlugin: {
      enabled: true,
      watchPaths: ['**/apps/*.yaml', '**/dialogs/**/*.yaml']
    }
  }
```
